rows.label: tlk44100184_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, outlanders! Come and
see! Look - it's a patch of
green! Isn't it amazing?!

rows.label: tlk44100184_01_msg0002
rows.name:
We hardly get any green here in
Luxuria. Not outside town anyway.

rows.label: tlk44100184_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I, uh, I really like plants.
But we're not allowed to leave
Luxuria to find any...

rows.label: tlk44100184_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I wish I could go out and see all the
plants I read about in the library.
But it's kind of impossible, huh...
